    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Xpressbees International Enterprises. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Digital Marketing Manager to strengthen our Navi Mumbai-based team.\n\nAbout Xpressbees International Enterprises:\nXpressbees International Enterprises is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Navi Mumbai, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Xpressbees International Enterprises!",
